"{\"uid\": \"straitstimes.com-sport-usa-skaters-want-2022-gold-medal-ceremony-at-paris-olympics\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Choose edition  Search  singapore  asia  world  opinion  life  business  sport  Visual  Podcasts  SPH Rewards  STClassifieds  Paid press releases  Advertise with us  FAQs  Contact us  Sign up now:Get the biggest sports news in your inbox  Madison Chock (left) and Evan Bates receiving their medals after the championship free dance at the 2024 US Figure Skating Championships.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 376, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 98, \"end\": 101, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"score\": 0.999999999996362, \"rank\": 3.568185162857051e-12, \"text\": \"SPH\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Singapore_Press_Holdings\"}, {\"begin\": 147, \"end\": 156, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"score\": 0.9604822703097123, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Advertise\", \"types\": [\"Q7377\", \"Q729\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Advertise_(horse)\"}, {\"begin\": 239, \"end\": 252, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madison Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}, {\"begin\": 264, \"end\": 274, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evan Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: REUTERS  PublishedJan 31, 2024, 04:28 PM  UpdatedJan 31, 2024, 10:15 PM  WASHINGTON-United States' figure skaters, who have been awarded gold after Kamila Valieva was disqualified from the 2022 Winter Olympics, said on Jan 30 they want a ceremony at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 378, \"to\": 654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 533, \"end\": 539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamila_Thompson\", \"score\": 0.9999999999899956, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kamila\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamila_Thompson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kamila_Thompson\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reigning ice dance world champions Evan Bates and Madison Chock were among nine Americans who became 2022 Beijing Olympic team figure skating champions after Valieva, part of the winning Russian team,received a four-year doping banfrom the Court of Arbitration for Sport (CAS) on Jan 29.\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Evan Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}, {\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 719, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Madison Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}, {\"begin\": 757, \"end\": 769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"2022 Beijing\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2022_Winter_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 843, \"end\": 850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.6931570207409335, \"rank\": 0.44072046000855986, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Medals have yet to be awarded and Chock and her teammates want to receive the medals in an Olympic atmosphere as soon as possible.\", \"from\": 945, \"to\": 1075, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 979, \"end\": 984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4190159683055996e-37, \"text\": \"Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have thought about it,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1114, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We would like to have a true Olympic medal ceremony.\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1168, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For us, that would be a ceremony at the Paris Olympics this summer... surrounded by the Olympic spirit.\", \"from\": 1169, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That would be the dream scenario.\\\"\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Following CAS' decision, Valieva being dropped from Russia's team scoring lifted the US squad into the gold medal spot in a re-ranking announced on Jan 29 by the International Skating Union (ISU).\", \"from\": 1311, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1321, \"end\": 1324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3251877413469633e-32, \"text\": \"CAS\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Court_of_Arbitration_for_Sport\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966764445882951, \"rank\": 0.0033125050607109158, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1396, \"end\": 1398, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9586309771001664, \"rank\": 0.04271627618279741, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1495, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999989286152, \"rank\": 9.773946088471252e-10, \"text\": \"Union\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1502, \"end\": 1505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.593792106601641e-32, \"text\": \"ISU\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Skating_Union\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Japan moved into silver with Russia third.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1509, \"end\": 1514, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.8435624845265832, \"rank\": 0.1693776960252855, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1538, \"end\": 1544, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.9966764445882951, \"rank\": 0.0033125050607109158, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Appeals could be pending but Sarah Hirshland, chief executive officer of the US Olympic & Paralympic Committee, said she was instructed she could award American skaters the gold medals.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"score\": 0.991078837482534, \"rank\": 0.00730258692900634, \"text\": \"Sarah\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sarah_Jane_Smith\"}, {\"begin\": 1630, \"end\": 1632, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9586309771001664, \"rank\": 0.04271627618279741, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1705, \"end\": 1713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999999334224889, \"rank\": 6.511633366672198e-08, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have been given clear direction we should proceed with giving medals to the US team and that's what we are going to do,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1819, \"end\": 1821, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9586309771001664, \"rank\": 0.04271627618279741, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no scenario in which Team USA is not the gold medal winner and we are eager to get these medals awarded.\", \"from\": 1874, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1905, \"end\": 1913, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.6694687408976994, \"rank\": 0.23368328530247098, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Everybody has a sense of urgency.\\\"\", \"from\": 1989, \"to\": 2023, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Chock added that when the controversy first unfolded two years ago, she never expected it would take this long to resolve.\", \"from\": 2025, \"to\": 2147, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There was a small underlying feeling of disappointment and sadness,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not realise it had been weighing on us the whole time until we got the resolution.\", \"from\": 2229, \"to\": 2318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's like a weight has been lifted.\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2356, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like we are celebrating our Olympic experience all over again.\", \"from\": 2357, \"to\": 2424, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It puts a feeling of closure to this whole movement and the Beijing Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2425, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And at age 31, Chock can finally call herself an Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2520, \"end\": 2525, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4190159683055996e-37, \"text\": \"Chock\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madison_Chock\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Amazing, quite frankly,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"A feeling I have always dreamt of, one I almost can not believe is finally here.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It has been a very happy 24 hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2726, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bates added that the past day had been \\\"surreal\\\" and unbelievable\\\" after the long delay.\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.576265741259716e-17, \"text\": \"Bates\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13219587\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Evan_Bates\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was a long and arduous wait,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2818, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope this team will be remembered as much for how we have handled this off the ice as much as for the performances we put on the ice.\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2997, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"AFP  Winter sports  Olympics 2024  United States  E-paper  Newsletters  Podcasts  RSS Feed  About Us  Terms & Conditions  Personal Data Protection Notice  Need help?\", \"from\": 2997, \"to\": 3163, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3033, \"end\": 3046, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9556587819419644, \"rank\": 0.03964360844814612, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 3080, \"end\": 3088, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"RSS Feed\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RSS\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 3164, \"to\": 3178, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 3180, \"to\": 3197, \"entities\": []}]}"